{"type": "article", "id": 23199, "title": "hotpot 热能锅", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-03T07:30:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607120554MhPd8lkEz2CBWOpT.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一款用软木制成的热能锅，德国设计师 May Kukula 以节约资源为出发点设计。需要先在火炉上加热，但只需平时三分之一的时间。然后放在热能锅里，软木材质的保温性能让它保持持续蒸煮的状态，是降低能耗的方式。此外，浅色的软木和黑色的帖和白瓷搭配起来时，非常清新居家。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120552d3BhaI8xwtUkzc45.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67114914\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120552aIm9Nr6xJA2M5VuU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67114914\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120553Yk9wKR3uB2WfnzjF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4400978\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 565px; width: 375px; left: 537px; top: 2022px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120553j7rNVWO6LI8G1oMz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50611247\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}